title: Flv.Recorder.2.0.1.315.Incl.Keygen-ONY
description:
APPLICATION : Flv Recorder 2.0.1.315 Incl Keygen
         OS : Win
       TYPE : Video Recorder
        WWW : http://www.flvrecorder.com
    RELDATE : 12/03/2008
 PROTECTION : Aspack / Serial
 CRKRELDATE : 09/04/2008

INSTALLATION: Install.
              Use keygen to generate your "Site License" serial.

       NOTES: 
              The name function in the keygen has the only purpose
              to make your serial unique to you. You can still register
              Flv Recorder with any name with the generated key.
              Please use chars like a-z and/or numbers. Chars like %_# )]/!
              will work but might be banned in future versions.
              
              Nuff said. Enjoy! / ONY

       ABOUT:

              Flv Recorder - the best Flv video grabber that can save/download/
              capture/grab/record flv video and audio streaming through HTTP and
              RTMP protocol.

              FlvRecorder have a excellent build-in Free Flv Player and help you
              watch flv videos, and it is pretty and easy to use.
              
              Best Features:

              * Can Record RTMP Flash Video
              
              * Can Record HTTP Flash Video
              
              * Build-in Flv Player
              
              * Sniff the Flash video address
              
              * Rename automatically
              
              * Record Multi Flash video
